Exception Summary
IdentifierCollisionException Thrown to indicate reuse of an Identifier.
MessageInvalidException Thrown when an FCP message is invalid.
NotAllowedException Thrown when a client tries to upload a file it's not allowed to upload (or otherwise read it), or download to a file which it's not allowed to download to (or otherwise write to).
PersistenceParseException Thrown when a persistent request cannot be parsed.
